F_x
F_y
F_z
(0,\sqrt{\pi},1)
0 = F_x(0,\sqrt{\pi},1)(x-0) + F_y(0,\sqrt{\pi},1)(y-\sqrt{\pi}) + F_z(0,\sqrt{\pi},1)(z-1)
